Description: Enterprise SCAP compliance scanning platform - Native deployment
 OpenWatch is an enterprise-grade compliance scanning platform powered by
 Kensa. This package provides native systemd deployment without requiring
 Docker or Podman containers. All components run directly on the host.
 .
 Key features:
  * Kensa-powered compliance scanning (508 YAML rules)
  * Multi-host fleet management via SSH
  * CIS, STIG, NIST 800-53, PCI-DSS, FedRAMP framework support
  * Real-time compliance dashboards
  * Role-based access control
  * Audit logging and reporting
  * Native systemd service management
 .
 Deployment: Backend API via uvicorn (FastAPI), Celery workers with Redis
 broker, PostgreSQL 15+ database, nginx serving React SPA. All services
 managed via systemctl.
 .
 Supports Ubuntu 24.04 LTS and newer.
